### ============================
### 订单（顾客）
### ============================

GET {{baseUrl}}/orders?page=1&limit=20&status=pending
Authorization: {{token}}
# 获取当前用户订单列表（分页+状态筛选）

### 创建订单
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}
# 从购物车创建，原子扣库存+清购物车
{
  "address": "北京市朝阳区xxx"
}

### 获取订单详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/1
Authorization: {{token}}
# 含订单明细

### 取消订单
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/1/cancel
Authorization: {{token}}
# 仅 pending 状态可取消，自动回退库存

